---

---

<section class="section" id="contacto">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label">Hablemos</p>

    <div class="contact-inner">
      <div class="contact-text">
        <h2 class="section-title">¿Tienes un proyecto<br /><em>en mente?</em></h2>
        <p>
          Estoy abierto a nuevas oportunidades, colaboraciones y proyectos freelance. Si tienes
          datos que necesitan análisis o un dashboard que construir, escríbeme.
        </p>

        <a href="mailto:edgar@email.com" class="email-link">
          edgar@email.com
          <svg
            width="16"
            height="16"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.5"
          >
            <path d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H7M17 7v10"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-links">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/edgar-ramxs"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="contact-social"
        >
          <span class="social-label">GitHub</span>
          <svg
            width="16"
            height="16"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.5"
          >
            <path d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H7M17 7v10"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://linkedin.com/in/edgar-ramxs"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="contact-social"
        >
          <span class="social-label">LinkedIn</span>
          <svg
            width="16"
            height="16"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.5"
          >
            <path d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H7M17 7v10"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .contact-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: end;
    padding: 4rem;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .contact-text p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 440px;
  }

  .email-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    transition: gap 0.2s;
  }

  .email-link:hover {
    gap: 0.9rem;
  }

  .contact-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: flex-end;
  }

  .contact-social {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    transition: color 0.2s;
    padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 2px;
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  .contact-social:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .contact-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding: 2rem;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .contact-links {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }
</style>
